data.description: Welcome to this charming 4bd, 1bth home built in 1961, nestled in the heart of the Northend. Just a leisurely stroll from the local elementary school, this home beckons you to step inside and start a new chapter of cherished memories. Boasting a spacious layout, the home flaunts a roomy primary suite that promises tranquility. The galley-style kitchen exudes charm & practicality, seamlessly flowing into a large dining area, perfect for both cozy family dinners and festive gatherings. Recent updates elevate this home above the rest: a tastefully remodeled bathroom, fresh carpeting in the living room, contemporary interior lighting, and pristine new doors. Experience peace of mind with a slew of upgraded essentials including a newer AC unit, revamped furnace internals, modernized main line plumbing, a recent water heater, and more. All your major concerns have been pre-emptively addressed! The exterior is equally delightful and offers and abundance of space! Additional amenities include RV parking & workshop!
